Summary: Five amber lights in a triangle shape moving north, northeast
divs: Sighting DetailsI was letting my dog outside in the backyard and saw five amber lights in a triangle formation heading north slowly. After a while they flickered out. I see these lights several times over a course of a year and have been for about 8 years now. They always head north to northeast. It has become no big deal since people here see them often. They are definetly NOT commercial aircraft of any kind.
